Subject: [PATCH 6/9] feat: add android-shims module

This module contains the shimmed versions of various classes modified
to adapt to the Android runtime. The module works in coordination of
the analysis-api-standalone-embeddable-for-ide module to replace usages
of the original classes with the shimmed variants.

Signed-off-by: Akash Yadav <akashyadav@appdevforall.org>
